e, and I now know about responsible disclosure.\",\"position\":{\"start\":{\"line\":23,\"column\":1,\"offset\":3316},\"end\":{\"line\":23,\"column\":216,\"offset\":3531}}}],\"position\":{\"start\":{\"line\":23,\"column\":1,\"offset\":3316},\"end\":{\"line\":23,\"column\":216,\"offset\":3531}}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":\"\\n\"},{\"type\":\"element\",\"tagName\":\"p\",\"properties\":{},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":\"At this point, the source code gained through source maps was not widespread knowledge, and was mostly contained, and I did not want it to spread any further before Cohost staff fixed it. After seeing the post from \"},{\"type\":\"element\",\"tagName\":\"Mention\",\"properties\":{\"handle\":\"staff\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":\"@staff\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":\" about it sucking to discover a bug on the weekends seeing it actively being used (\"},{\"type\":\"element\",\"tagName\":\"a\",\"properties\":{\"href\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fcohost.org\u002Fstaff\u002Fpost\u002F294956-minor-update-to-the\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fcohost.org\u002Fstaff\u002Fpost\u002F294956-minor-update-to-the\",\"position\":{\"start\":{\"line\":25,\"column\":305,\"offset\":3837},\"end\":{\"line\":25,\"column\":361,\"offset\":3893}}}],\"position\":{\"start\":{\"line\":25,\"column\":305,\"offset\":3837},\"end\":{\"line\":25,\"column\":361,\"offset\":3893}}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":\") I realized that I had definitely made some mistakes along the way.\",\"position\":{\"start\":{\"line\":25,\"column\":361,\"offset\":3893},\"end\":{\"line\":25,\"column\":429,\"offset\":3961}}}],\"position\":{\"start\":{\"line\":25,\"column\":1,\"offset\":3533},\"end\":{\"line\":25,\"column\":429,\"offset\":3961}}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":\"\\n\"},{\"type\":\"element\",\"tagName\":\"p\",\"properties\":{},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":\"I waited until Monday (today as of writing) for Cohost staff to see my support ticket, and after noticing that the staff member who fixed the bug (\"},{\"type\":\"element\",\"tagName\":\"Mention\",\"properties\":{\"handle\":\"vogon\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":\"@vogon\"}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":\") had replied to an earlier post I made, I \"},{\"type\":\"element\",\"tagName\":\"a\",\"properties\":{\"href\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fcohost.org\u002Fmintexists\u002Fpost\u002F295914-it-s-so-cool-seeing\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":\"replied to their reply\",\"position\":{\"start\":{\"line\":27,\"column\":198,\"offset\":4160},\"end\":{\"line\":27,\"column\":220,\"offset\":4182}}}],\"position\":{\"start\":{\"line\":27,\"column\":197,\"offset\":4159},\"end\":{\"line\":27,\"column\":284,\"offset\":4246}}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":\" to let them know about the probably urgent bug of the source code availability. This got my ticket through to them, and they let me know that it would be fixed, and that once it was, I could make this post about how I found the issue!\",\"position\":{\"start\":{\"line\":27,\"column\":284,\"offset\":4246},\"end\":{\"line\":27,\"column\":519,\"offset\":4481}}}],\"position\":{\"start\":{\"line\":27,\"column\":1,\"offset\":3963},\"end\":{\"line\":27,\"column\":519,\"offset\":4481}}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":\"\\n\"},{\"type\":\"element\",\"tagName\":\"h3\",\"properties\":{},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":\"In Conclusion \"},{\"type\":\"element\",\"tagName\":\"CustomEmoji\",\"properties\":{\"name\":\"eggbug\",\"url\":\"https:\u002F\u002Fcohost.org\u002Fstatic\u002F17aa2d48956926005de9.png\"},\"children\":[]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":\"\"}],\"position\":{\"start\":{\"line\":29,\"column\":1,\"offset\":4483},\"end\":{\"line\":29,\"column\":27,\"offset\":4509}}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":\"\\n\"},{\"type\":\"element\",\"tagName\":\"p\",\"properties\":{},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":\"I think the biggest thing I learned from this whole experie